2013; wrong! Uzbekistan&#x2019;s rail network is a super convenient, affordable and overall great way to get around the country. The fast-trains are from the same quality as Italy or another European country.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Right now, booking tickets online is still very difficult (2019) but fortunately, Advantour, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.advantour.com\/uzbekistan\/trains.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"the silk road tour operator (opens in a new tab)\">the silk road tour operator<\/a>, takes away the hassle by pre-booking everything for you.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130539\/train-tashkent-samarkand-uzbekistan.jpg\" alt=\"train tashkent samarkand uzbekistan\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"301\" alt=\"train tashkent samarkand uzbekistan\" class=\"wp-image-17309 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130539\/train-tashkent-samarkand-uzbekistan.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130539\/train-tashkent-samarkand-uzbekistan-300x201.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130539\/train-tashkent-samarkand-uzbekistan-600x402.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\