__inner-container\">\n<p>All major cities are connected with a domestic or international airport and have regularly scheduled flights. Right now, we would only advise taking a flight to go back from Khiva to Tashkent because the train between the other cities is a much better way of traveling.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125716\/best-travel-time-uzbekistan-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"best travel time uzbekistan\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best travel time uzbekistan\" data-id=\"17859\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=17859\" class=\"wp-image-17859 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125716\/best-travel-time-uzbekistan-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125716\/best-travel-time-uzbekistan-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125716\/best-travel-time-uzbekistan-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125716\/best-travel-time-uzbekistan-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125716\/best-travel-time-uzbekistan-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125716\/best-travel-time-uzbekistan-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125716\/best-travel-time-uzbekistan-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125716\/best-travel-time-uzbekistan-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/23125716\